Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.86,0:01:59.05,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}我想了解一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.19,0:02:03.14,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}说给我听
